Hermione Jean Granger (/hɜːrˈmaɪ.əni/ / ˈɡreɪndʒər /) ke setaki se iqapetsoeng letotong la J. K. Rowling's Harry Potter. O hlaha ka lekhetlo la pele ho Harry Potter le Lejoe la Philosopher, e le seithuti se secha tseleng e eang Hogwarts. Kamora hore Harry le Ron ba mo pholohele ho tsoa lithabeng ka kamoreng ea ho phomola ea banana, o ba metsoalle e meholo 'me hangata o sebelisa tsebo ea hae e potlakileng, boipolelo ba tsebo le tsebo ea boiphetetso ho thusa maemong a mahlonoko. Rowling o boletse hore Hermione e tšoana le ngoanana e monyane, ka ts'ireletso ea hae le ts'abo ea ho se atlehe.

Sebopeho sena se tumme haholo. Mofuta oa Hermione o hlahisitsoeng ke Emma Watson lifiliming tsohle tse robeli tsa Harry Potter ho tloha Lejoeng la Philosopher ka 2001 ho ea fihla ho Deathly Hallows - Karolo ea 2 ka 2011 e ile ea khethoa e le semelo se setle sa basali nakong eohle ho phetho e entsoeng har'a litsebi tsa Hollywood ke The Hollywood Reporter ka 2016.
